originalText.text:
A world-class nutritional therapist.
Michelle has been working with our dance students for the past 10 months. Her passion and knowledge combined with her endless creativity have been incredibly impactful for our students - from guidance on diet choices, to instilling healthy habits and becoming artists conscious of their bodies.
Her personal approach, positive energy, and love for others are unmatchable.

originalText.text: Michelle is the absolute best! I am the healthiest and happiest I've ever been working with her. In just a matter of weeks, she has helped me achieve more energy/alertness, balanced blood sugar, better digestion, more range of motion and strength, regular menstrual cycles, and overall a feeling of peace with my body. Michelle is a delightful enthusiastic food lover who has helped me solve lifelong health issues. I've seen many specialists and doctors over the years, but Michelle is the person I'd recommend to anyone to feel their best. Her patience and extensive knowledge on how food affects the body are incomparable.
